ji\" /><br />\n用盡你一切方法動員認識既人星期日出嚟堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411f0d744e32f602df0850ecc01c76f557034b30","tid":1224153,"uid":242657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 不撤不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"6faf12c23f132fa7f3dfdbc1af18f804e0bd825c","tid":1224153,"uid":176017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:43:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fbe2c4efcaeabb77f311629fb0611cf195cc9d7","tid":1224153,"uid":41342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:44:03.000Z","msg":"6月16日再遊行<br />\n四大訴求：<br />\n1. 撤回引渡方案<br />\n2. 釋放被捕義士<br />\n3. 追究暴力黑警<br />\n4. 政官問責下台<br />\n<br />\n得一個暫緩點收貨？<br />\n點對得住受傷既示威者？<br />\n警察做野可以無後果？<br />\n政官搞壇咁既野都無事？<br />\n<br />\n616不撤不散"},{"pid":"d33b294c2d78c096985fda956c2b24c773a6b035","tid":1224153,"uid":146493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:44:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5ab37ab60a3cd5c8502e57a79781327c44f6131","tid":1224153,"uid":111578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0113e615fb3d201e60335b66f726d0b641e29cd","tid":1224153,"uid":6786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b180b8761fe341a5125d14b41f1c1943aadf4c84","tid":1224153,"uid":242657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">星期日 不撤不散</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1bb041fe34db78e281942351f54ae78eb7917f7","tid":1224153,"uid":63331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebeeb9e4a9f5c603e08cfce