:0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"○三年七一遊行有逾五十萬人上街，但港府事後僅修訂三項廿三條草案內容，堅拒撤回立法，泛民隨即發動在七月九日包圍立法會。在龐大反對壓力及暴動危機下，時任自由黨主席田北俊於七月六日晚上宣布辭去行政會議成員職務，該黨八名立法會議員將反對草案恢復二讀。港府最終於七月七日凌晨宣布<ins><strong>撤回</strong></ins>廿三條立法。<br />\n<br />\n在二○一二年，特區政府計劃把「德育及國民教育科」列為中小學必修科，被外界質疑是政治「洗腦」，反對團體同年七月發起遊行，逾萬人上街，至九月多個團體在政府總部舉行反國教集會，聲稱逾十二萬人參加，時任特首梁振英翌日宣布<ins><strong>撤回</strong></ins>計劃，承諾五年任期內不再推動國民教育科獨立成科。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%B7%AA%E4%BD%8E%E6%9C%89%E5%85%88%E4%BE%8B-%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%9923%E6%A2%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%86%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E-214500562.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Famphtml%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E8%25B7%25AA%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2595%259923%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%259A%2586%25E6%2592%25A4%25E5%259B%259E-214500562.html&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=2e67d49d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/hk.news.yahoo.com/amphtml/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E8%B7%AA%E4%BD%8E%E6%9C%89%E5%85%88%E4%BE%8B-%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%9923%E6%A2%9D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%86%E6%92%A4%E5%9B%9E-214500562.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔撒回就隨時繼續架啦"},{"pid":"b7660261b583beb64a879a76f9ff173ff129ba88","tid":1224153,"uid":242657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e3dc9f7a565713f9127d569c44a553d987c1b5b","tid":1224153,"uid":111093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"屋企group已經打曬飛機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"長輩圖用左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7fe6ae5dc12f5b7aab452566f8fa91361afa413","tid":1224153,"uid":242657,"lik